#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:2
msgid "Inspect locational marginal prices"
msgstr "查看节点边际电价 (LMP)"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:4
msgid ""
"**Goal.** Read PREP-SHOT's :term:`LMP` output and use it to diagnose "
"binding constraints, compare zones, and back-cast wholesale-price "
"trajectories."
msgstr "**目标。** 读取 PREP-SHOT 的 :term:`LMP` 输出,用以诊断起作用的约束、比较区域差异、回溯批发电价轨迹。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:8
msgid ""
"LMPs are the dual of the nodal power-balance constraint -- the marginal "
"cost of one extra MWh of demand at each ``(hour, month, year, zone)``. "
"PREP-SHOT exposes them as ``shadow_price_demand`` in the result NetCDF "
"since v1.9.1."
msgstr ""
"LMP 是节点功率平衡约束的对偶变量——在每个 ``(hour, month, year, zone)`` 处多供一兆瓦时需求的边际成本。自 "
"v1.9.1 起,PREP-SHOT 将其作为 ``shadow_price_demand`` 写入结果 NetCDF。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:14
msgid "Recipe"
msgstr "做法"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:38
msgid "Sign convention"
msgstr "符号约定"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:40
msgid ""
"LMPs in ``shadow_price_demand`` are **positive when serving more demand "
"is more expensive** -- the standard convention used by PyPSA, Switch, and"
" GenX. PREP-SHOT internally flips the raw HiGHS dual (which is negative "
"because the demand-balance constraint is posed as ``demand - supply == "
"0``) before writing the NetCDF."
msgstr ""
"``shadow_price_demand`` 中的 LMP **当满足更多需求更昂贵时为正**——这是 PyPSA、Switch、GenX "
"等模型采用的标准约定。PREP-SHOT 在写入 NetCDF 前会内部翻转 HiGHS 原始对偶值的符号 (原始值为负,因为需求平衡约束写作 "
"``demand - supply == 0``)。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:47
msgid "NPV vs real-year prices"
msgstr "净现值 vs 实际年度价格"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:49
msgid ""
"LMPs are written in **NPV-discounted USD per MWh**. To recover "
"undiscounted real-year prices, divide by the variable-cost factor for "
"that year and zone:"
msgstr "LMP 以 **净现值折现的 USD/MWh** 写入。如要恢复未折现的实际年度价格,需除以对应年份和区域的可变成本系数:"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:61
msgid ""
"For most analyses (relative-zone comparisons, peak-hour identification, "
"trend over the planning horizon), the NPV scaling is harmless and keeps "
"the cross-zone comparison meaningful."
msgstr "对大多数分析 (区域间相对比较、峰值时段识别、规划期内趋势) 而言,NPV 折现是无害的,并能保持跨区域比较的可信度。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:66
msgid "Common pitfalls"
msgstr "常见陷阱"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:68
msgid ""
"**MIP solves don't return duals.** If ``shadow_price_demand`` is missing "
"from the NetCDF, the solve was a MIP (or infeasible). The v1.9.1 "
"extraction is wrapped in try/except: a warning logs and the variable is "
"omitted rather than crashing the run."
msgstr ""
"**MIP 求解不返回对偶值。** 若 NetCDF 中缺少 ``shadow_price_demand``,说明本次求解是 MIP "
"(或不可行)。v1.9.1 的提取过程包在 try/except 中:会记录警告并省略该变量,而不会导致运行崩溃。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:72
msgid ""
"**Storage zones distort short-horizon LMPs.** A binding storage state-of-"
"charge constraint shows up as an LMP spike in one hour and a depression "
"in another (energy-arbitrage). Don't read a single hour's LMP as \"the "
"price\"; average over a day or week."
msgstr ""
"**储能区域会扭曲短期 LMP。** 起作用的储能荷电状态约束会在某个小时表现为 LMP 尖峰,而在另一时刻表现为洼地 "
"(能量套利)。不要把单一小时的 LMP 当作 \"电价\";应当按日或按周取平均。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:76
msgid ""
"**Demand profile shape matters.** PREP-SHOT samples representative "
"hours/months. The LMPs you get reflect the sampled hours, not the full "
"8760-hour year. A handful of representative peak hours can dominate the "
"average."
msgstr ""
"**需求曲线形状很重要。** PREP-SHOT 使用典型小时 / 月。所得 LMP 反映的是被采样的小时,而非完整的 8760 "
"小时全年。少数几个典型峰值小时可能主导平均值。"

#: ../../source/how_to/inspect_lmps.rst:81
msgid ""
"For the underlying constraint (``power_balance_cons`` in "
"``prepshot/_model/demand.py``), see :doc:`../Mathematical_notations`."
msgstr ""
"底层约束 (``prepshot/_model/demand.py`` 中的 ``power_balance_cons``) 参见 "
":doc:`../Mathematical_notations`。"

